<body id="page-top">
   
    <!-- About Section-->
    <section class="page-section" style="background-color:#E5F0FF; color:#101F90;" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- About Section Heading-->
            <h2 class="page-section-heading text-center text-uppercase mt-3"><br>About Us</h2>
            <!-- Icon Divider-->
            <div class="divider-custom divider-light">
                <div class="divider-custom-line"></div>
                <div class="divider-custom-icon"><i class="fas fa-star"></i></div>
                <div class="divider-custom-line"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- About Section Content-->
            <div class="row" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-md-center"><img class="img-test" src="assets/img/about/team.png" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-md-center"><img class="img-test" src="assets/img/about/expert.png" alt="..." /></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-xl-center"><p class="lead"><h2>Our <br> Commitment</h2></p></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-xl-center"><p class="lead"><h2>Expert Care with a Personal Touch</h2></p></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-md-center"><p class="lead">At the heart of our clinic is a commitment to putting patients first. We understand that visiting a medical facility can be a daunting experience, and that's why we have designed our space to radiate comfort and positivity. From our cozy waiting area to our friendly and caring staff, every element of Addicure has been carefully crafted to ensure your visit is as stress-free as possible.</p></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-md-center"><p class="lead">Led by a team of experienced and compassionate healthcare professionals, Addicure offers a comprehensive range of medical services to address your individual needs. Whether you're seeking routine check-ups, specialized treatments, or health advice, our dedicated staff is here to listen, understand, and guide you through every step of your healthcare journey.</p></div>

            </div>

            <div class="row" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-md-center"><img class="img-test" src="assets/img/about/collab.png" alt="..." /></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-md-center"><img class="img-test" src="assets/img/about/inclusive.png" alt="..." /></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-xl-center"><p class="lead"><h2>Community and Collaboration</h2></p></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-xl-center"><p class="lead"><h2>A Welcoming Space for All</h2></p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 ms-auto text-md-center"><p class="lead">We believe that healthcare is not just about treating ailments; it's about building a healthy community. That's why we encourage open communication and collaboration between patients and our medical experts. We take the time to listen to your concerns, answer your questions, and involve you in decisions about your health.</p></div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 me-auto text-md-center"><p class="lead">Diversity and inclusivity are at the core of our values. Our clinic is a safe space where everyone is treated with respect and dignity, regardless of their background, identity, or medical needs. We're dedicated to creating an environment where you can feel comfortable discussing your health, no matter your age, gender, or cultural background.</p></div>

            </div>
            <div class="row" style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="col-md-4 mx-auto" style="display: inline-block;"><img class="img-test" src="assets/img/about/wellness.png" alt="..." /></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 mx-auto text-xl-center"><p class="lead"><h2>Join Us in Your Journey to Wellness</h2></p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4 mx-auto text-md-center"><p class="lead">Whether you're a long-time patient or new to our clinic, we are excited to be a part of your journey to better health and wellness. Addicure is not just a medical facility; it's a place where relationships are built, smiles are shared, and positive health outcomes are achieved.</p></div>
            </div>

            <!-- About Section Button-->
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a class="btn btn-xl btn-outline-light" style="background-color:#101F90;" a href="appointment.html">
                    <i class="fas fa-download me-2"></i>
                    Book an appointment now!
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Footer-->
    <footer class="footer text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Footer Location-->
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                    <h4 class="text-uppercase mb-4">Location</h4>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">
                        2215 John Daniel Drive
                        <br />
                        Clark, MO 65243
                    </p>
                </div>
                <!-- Footer Social Icons-->
                <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                    <h4 class="text-uppercase mb-4">ADDICURE</h4>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-social mx-1" href="#!"><i class="fab fa-fw fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-social mx-1" href="#!"><i class="fab fa-fw fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-social mx-1" href="#!"><i class="fab fa-fw fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-social mx-1" href="#!"><i class="fab fa-fw fa-dribbble"></i></a>
                </div>
                <!-- Footer About Text-->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <h4 class="text-uppercase mb-4">About the Clinic</h4>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">
                        ADDICURE is a clinic that helps you with your specific medical needs. We provide cutting-edge services for medications and facilities for your wellness.

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
